lgp.core.evolution

Interface Solution<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    IrisSolution, SimpleFunctionSolution, SimpleFunctionSolution, SinPolySolution

    public Solution<T>

    Represents a solution to a problem.

    The interface is left open so that when defining one's problem, it is straight-forward to define the format of the solution, as it will probably depend on the use case on what the solution should actually contain.
